room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: Human Trials proved to be difficult and we loved it.

room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: We've done the other rooms at the Panic Room so we kind of knew what to expect, or so we thought. Human Trials blew us away with its unique puzzles, and surprises. Our Game Master Rachel was the best and her excitement for the room made it all the better. I love when Game Guides love their rooms! Awesome room, just sad we've played the others, I hope they get a new room soon!

room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: Super fun! Did the human trials and it was very challenging but will be back for another room challenge soon!

room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: Went with a group of friends and solved the Human Trials Room. I was initially worried we wouldn't make it out but we did!! It was my first time there, but the staff, shout out to Claudia, was very friendly and helpful! Thanks for the experience!!

room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: I went with a group and did the Human Trials room. The room was fun and gave us many thought-provoking challenges. Our group had a lot of fun and learned to work well together. We managed to solve the room, but only with help from our operator Claudia. She did a great job, provided useful hints, and gave us a very thorough run through of the room afterwards.
